## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives on the topic. The search was limited to English-language sources, which may exclude relevant insights from non-English publications. Additionally, the dynamic nature of organizational culture means that the impact of future plans can vary significantly across different organizations and industries.

